title: Statement by the Press Secretary on H.J.Res. 78 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
December 16, 2015

 



Statement by the Press Secretary on H.J.Res. 78





	On Wednesday, December 16, 2015, the President signed into law:

	H.J.Res. 78, which provides fiscal year 2016 appropriations for continuing projects and activities of the Federal Government through Tuesday, December 22, 2015.
